tip.text: This peach walnut torte is truly divine!!!
Had a flat white. It's alright. I duno, it tasted a little rough in taste and texture unlike the ones i had at toby's.

formattedAddress: Dr. A. Santos Ave (at Sucat Rd)

tip.text: They don't get cheap on making ur salad (havent tried the wrap yet).Hefty serving indeed.Their salad is a bit pricey but, heck, i'd still come back coz it's really deelish... And yeah, healthy too!
I find their pulled pork belly rice really yummy! Just perfect for postduty grub. #comfortfood
Delicious and juicy ribs at a surprisingly affordable price. 1 slab of ribs and 2 side dishes (good for 2) for only 390! Not bad,eh?😊
Seafood laksa pasta-- it's a must try!
Still the best pares for me!
Chocolate truffle cake is the 💣💣💣.... Chocolatey goodness!!!
First time to try 8 cuts and I must say, other than their good tastin' burgers, they have awesome customer service too! Anyway, never leave here without trying the Piggy! 🐷
Don't leave without trying their chocolate lava cake! Super gooey and chocolateeeey! Best eaten while hot. And yes, with a dollop of vanilla icecream.👌
Banana chocolate walnut muffin is a must try! 😊
